# Open Code Review Integration

When modifying code:
1. Before committing, run: `npx @opencodereview/cli scan ./src --sla L1`
2. Fix any critical/high severity issues before finalizing
3. For PR reviews, run: `npx @opencodereview/cli scan . --diff --base origin/main --head HEAD`

MCP Server available: npx @opencodereview/mcp-server
Tools: scan_directory, scan_diff, explain_issue, heal_code
